# Process Attributes

## process.executable.name

The name of the executable that started the process.

| Property | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Type | `string` |
| Has PII | false |
| Exists in OpenTelemetry | Yes |
| Example | `getsentry` |

| Property | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Type | `integer` |
| Has PII | false |
